com.rwbsystems.HiveUnitTesting.TestTemplates

Class TableTestBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rwbsystems.HiveUnitTesting.TestTemplates.TableTestBase
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DcLargeOnlineSalesHqlTest

    public abstract class TableTestBase
extends java.lang.Object
    An abstract class that can be used to automatically handle basic drop/create test logic. A class that wishes to automatically run drop/create test logic, just inherits the class and implements the abstract methods. Most methods are public so customized logic can be implemented and overridden.

        public void setupTestEnvironment()
